17 or system transmission operator to be used by the licensee;
18 3. a certification of compliance with applicable federal and
19 State environmental laws and regulations that relate to the generation of electricity; and
20 4. payment of the applicable licensing fee.
21 (2) (i) The term of a residential electricity supplier license is 3 years.
